MODE=scandoc
AE_LOCK=1
REPEAT_N=3
# SCAN DOCS does NOT enter a com.oplus.camera submode — it launches a SEPARATE app
# (com.coloros.ocrscanner / com.oplus.scanner.ui.main.CameraActivity). So com.oplus.camera APP-side probes
# are intentionally N/A for this condition. It IS a full provider+cameraserver session and the SERVER/PROVIDER
# probes capture it cleanly. Captured 2026-06-15 (V16.1.0):
#   getExtensionOperatingMode: arg_mode=0x1b5f2bc1 -> op_mode=0x8001  (OEM extension mode #1)
#   provider configure_streams: op_mode=0x8001, 9-then-8 OUTPUT streams, incl:
#     Y8 1440x1080 (usage 0x40)         -> grayscale CV/edge-detection (the doc-scan signature)
#     RAW_OPAQUE 4096x3072 (12MP) + RAW_OPAQUE 8192x6144 (50MP full-res)
#     YCbCr_420_888 1600x1200 / 4096x3072 (proc) + 320x240 (thumb)
# IDENTITY GATE — live-traced 2026-06-15 (frida on cameraserver, CameraServiceExtImpl::onTransact, export-
# resolved). During the scanner session these OEM binder codes FIRED (verified OBSERVATION):
#   10004 CLIENT_IS_AUTHED x1   (auth gate: isSystemCameraPkgName/isSystemCameraUid at connect)
#   10005 SET_CLIENT_INFO  x43  (per-request (pkg,uid,pid) identity stamp — NOT 10003 SET_PACKAGE_NAME)
#   10015 SEND_OPLUS_EXT_CAM_CMD x3 ; plus 10002/10006/10007/10016 session/feature traffic
# => com.coloros.ocrscanner is an OEM-identity client (passes the ExtImpl auth gate), which is what grants it
#    the extension op_mode=0x8001 pathway. libcsextimpl.so is ABSENT on LOS (dropped d654641) -> these codes
#    would return UNKNOWN_TRANSACTION(-38) and the client silently degrades to vanilla camera2.
# INFERENCE (not yet proven; needs OOS<->LOS A/B): that this auth gate is THE root granting the pathway, and
# the 0x1b5f2bc1->0x8001 token mapping (token not in repo; lives in OCS-SDK jar com.oplus.camera.unit.sdk.jar
# -> jadx target). Hook targets to prove: CameraServiceExtImpl::onTransact (codes), getExtensionOperatingMode
# (base+0x84818, vendor-tag UNK_00142f77 read), afterConnect (base+0x6d444, pkg/uid of connecting client).
NOTE="SCAN DOCS = separate app com.coloros.ocrscanner; provider/server denominator (op_mode=0x8001, 9-stream incl Y8 1440x1080 + 8192x6144 RAW_OPAQUE 50MP); app-side probes N/A by design"
EXTRA_PROBES="hook_configure_streams probe_get_extension_opmode"
